National Bureau of Statistics: From January to November, the total profit of industrial enterprises above designated size nationwide was 6667.48 billion yuan, a year-on-year decrease of 4.7%
From January to November, state-owned enterprises realized a total profit of 2038.77 billion yuan, a year-on-year decrease of 8.4%;
The total profit of joint-stock enterprises was 5014.30 billion yuan, a decrease of 5.7%
The total profit of foreign-invested enterprises and Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan-invested enterprises was 1606.29 billion yuan, a decrease of 0.8%;
The total profit of private enterprises was 1964.91 billion yuan, a decrease of 1.0%
